data.description: Stop the car! This 3 bedroom, 1 bath home right outside city limits is waiting for its new owners. Spacious and bright living room. Kitchen/dining combo that gives access to the back deck. Completing the upper level you have 3 nice sized bedrooms and a full bath. Finished basement houses a large family room, your laundry/utility room and the 1 car garage. You'll love the large yard, the 18x24 detached shop/garage and the off-street parking. Call today to schedule your showing.
